column1: Observations before October 7, 1896 are from the single Dow Jones Average and has been adjusted to merge with the rest of the data.
Observations from October 7, 1896 to July 30, 1914 are from the first DJIA and has been adjusted to merge with the second series.
Citation: Samuel H. Williamson, 'Daily Closing Value of the Dow Jones Average, 1885 to Present,' MeasuringWorth, 2022.
